description: This reactor powered long range survey and exploration vessel can house a small crew in relative comfort. Includes two adjacent air tight bays rated for science and engineering. Given the potentially volatile nature of the experiments done on the Ibex, the ship has additional redundancy in the form of two Nav stations in the standard design.
